data.description:
Seller is open to negotiations around financing options.  You'll be Amazed at the value in this 2618 sq ft home!  Prepare to be delighted with the beautiful designer accents and features in this 4 bedroom, 3 bath Richmond American Home.  This is a 1 year old home - no waiting or having to deal with the hassle/expense of installing a rear yard and window coverings. Both are already tastefully installed for you.  The entryway is inviting and as you walk in you’ll notice the abundance of natural light.  The entry is flanked by a ½ bath and the main floor office/bedroom.  Walking further into the home you come upon the Designer Kitchen with its White Cabinets, Quarts Counters, Large Island and Stainless Steel Appliances.  The kitchen also features a roomy Pantry and Eat-in area with Sliding Glass Wall System leading to the cozy covered patio in the rear – perfect for Entertaining!  The Family room is spacious and features a Designer Tile Surround Fireplace.  Moving up a level you’ll find a well laid out floorplan with 3 bedrooms 2 baths and a laundry room.  The 2 secondary bedrooms are roomy and with great closet space and they share a full size bathroom with a spacious counter top.  The large laundry room is perfect for storage as well.  A Generous sized Primary Bedroom features lots of space, a Stunning 4 piece bath, and an Oversized Walk-in closet.  The neighborhood is quiet and includes its own park with playground.  Convenient Loction – just minutes from I-76, shopping, recreation, and great schools. Priced to Sell! 
                                                                                                                                                                              


[Information provided herein is from sources deemed reliable but not guaranteed and is provided without the intention that any buyer rely upon it. Listing Broker takes no responsibility for its accuracy and all information must be independently verified by buyers.]
